        </profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-04-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-04-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="669" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d669">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.0031/4–1246</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by President <persName type="from">Truman</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-04-12">April 12,
                            1946</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I read your memorandum of the fourth in regard to Trade-agreement Negotiations
                    with a lot of interest and I approve your suggestions on informing the other
                    Governments.</p>
                <p>Have you any objection to my reading your whole memorandum to the Big Four next
                        Monday.<note n="61" xml:id="d669fn61">April 15.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>H[<hi rend="smallcaps">arry</hi>] S. T[<hi rend="smallcaps">ruman</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
